text: It was amazing that we got a deep conversation about singing from Jungkook. We've been waiting for this for so long. The interview revealed his singing knowledge and the way he discovers his own style....Anyone who reads Jungkook's interview today knows that he is a passionate, hardworking and educated person, not only as a musician as a human being. No matter how famous he is, he continues to develop himself, despite all the difficulties he faced from debuting now and the pressures he went through until now... perfect people like Jungkook always feel that they are not giving their best or lazy as he says simply because they are able to give better than that and they are able to achieve perfection.
